<div class="container mt-4">
    <h2>✅ Current Features</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Mobile-style design for a clean and simple workout tracking experience</li>
        <li>Categorzied List of Exercises</li>
        <li>Detailed set tracking accessibility (reps and weight)</li>
        <li>Automatic Workout Saving on Completion</li>
        <li>View past workouts with full breakdown</li>
        <li>Ability to Save Workouts Without an Account (Workout History Will Be Lost If Browser History is Deleted --> Highly Recommend Registering an Account</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="mt-4">🛠 Coming Soon</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Forgot Password Emails</li>
        <li>Progressive Web App (PWA) Installation Support</li>
        <li>User Profile Management (Update Email, Preferred Account Naming, Password, Delete Account)</li>
        <li>Custom Workout Naming</li>
        <li>Add Notes to Current or Saved Workouts</li>
        <li>Pause and Revisit Incomplete Workouts</li>
        <li>Search For Specific Exercises in Exercise Selection Modal</li>
        <li>Add Custom Exercises to Exercise Selection Modal</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="mt-4">🐞 Known Bugs / Issues</h2>
