        <li>Reset Password Emails Not Being Sent <STRONG>PLEASE WRITE DOWN YOUR PASSWORD FOR THE TIME BEING... THIS IS THE MAIN BUG RIGHT NOW</STRONG></li>
        <li>Incomplete Workouts Log Being Lost</li>
        <li>Duplication of Workouts When Finishing a Workout</li>
        <li>Initial load time on first visit can take a few seconds</li>
        <li>Some button tap targets may be small on iOS Safari</li>
    </ul>

